    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its initial purchase. The exterior features original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, free of any chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in an 'as-new' state; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear or creasing, and the original protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. Mechanically, it is flawless. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive binder of records included. The engine bay is concours-clean, and the undercarriage is remarkably free of road debris or corrosion. This is a collector-grade vehicle for the discerning buyer who demands perfection. Nonsmoker, no pets, and strictly hand-washed only.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
