      "description": "Presenting an exceptional opportunity to acquire an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been preserved in exemplary condition, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from its original showroom state. Meticulously maintained and mechanically superior, this unit represents the definitive standard for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
