      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, a masterclass in lightweight engineering and rotary performance. This specimen retains its original 13B-REW power plant, featuring the sophisticated sequential twin-turbocharger system that delivers smooth, surge-free power delivery. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise five-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Mechanically, the car is flawless; the cooling system is optimized while maintaining the stock appearance. The chassis exhibits perfect 50/50 weight distribution, complemented by unblemished double-wishbone suspension components. This is an investment-grade FD for the discerning collector who demands mechanical purity and factory-original specifications.",
